Roadmap towards v 4.0.0

[] API: possibilità di inserire funzioni da applicare ai nome del campo: count, avg, max

[] API: possibilità di aggiungere subquery nel nome del campo, es:
SELECT paths__geodata.geometry,
       (select count(*) from paths__m_msplaces where  place = paths__places.id) as "Tot. manuscripts",
       paths__places.id,
       paths__places.name,
       paths__places.pleiades,
       paths__places.typology
  FROM paths__places
       JOIN
       paths__geodata ON paths__geodata.table_link = 'paths__places' AND 
                         paths__geodata.id_link = paths__places.id
 WHERE paths__places.id IN (
           SELECT paths__m_msplaces.place
             FROM paths__m_msplaces
            WHERE paths__m_msplaces.table_link = 'paths__manuscripts' AND 
                  paths__m_msplaces.type = 'discovery'
       )
 LIMIT 500 OFFSET 0;


